Class RdKNNLeafEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.AbstractLeafEntry
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.spatial.SpatialPointLeafEntry
        • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.spatial.rstarvariants.rdknn.RdKNNLeafEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureVector<Number>, NumberVector, SpatialComparable, Entry, LeafEntry, RdKNNEntry, SpatialEntry, Externalizable, Serializable

    public class RdKNNLeafEntry
extends SpatialPointLeafEntry
implements RdKNNEntry
    Represents an entry in a leaf node of an RdKNN-Tree. Additionally to a SpatialLeafEntry a RdKNNLeafEntry holds the knn distance of the underlying data object.
    Author:
    Elke Achtert
